# Build context is the repo root for both service Dockerfiles. Keep it lean and
# never ship local state — installs and builds happen inside the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
# tsbuildinfo lives at the package root (not in dist), so it dodges the dist
# rule. Left in, a stale one makes composite tsc skip emit → no dist → the
# workspaces can't resolve each other's types. Never ship it.
**/*.tsbuildinfo
uploads
sample-itbs
.git
*.log
.env
.env.*
npm-debug.log*
